OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with cloud spreading
OL,7,Finland. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be dry and cloudy. Clearer across
OL,9,Fwestern Tayside until later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA dry day. Rather cloudy
OL,12,Fstart, but sunshine gradually
OL,13,Fincreasing from mid-morning. Best of
OL,14,Fthe sunshine across western Tayside
OL,15,Fand Stirling. Winds light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
